# Title: Potential File Overwrite Via Sysinternals SDelete
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2021-06-03
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the use of SDelete to erase a file not the free space
# MITRE Tactic: Impact
# Tags: attack.impact, attack.t1485
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_sysinternals_sdelete.yml

OriginalFileName="sdelete.exe" NOT (CommandLine IN ("* -h*", "* -c*", "* -z*", "* /?*"))